  "description": "A breathtaking nighttime view of a city skyline illuminated by vibrant fireworks. A long bridge stretches across dark water towards the city, its lights mirroring those of the buildings. The cityscape features a mix of high-rise buildings and architectural structures, with a distinct cluster of buildings that appear to resemble a sailboat. The fireworks display is in full bloom, with various colors including red, white, blue, and gold exploding against the dark sky. The scene is captured from a distance, emphasizing the scale of the city and the spectacle of the fireworks. Several red lights are visible along the water's edge, likely indicating navigational markers.",
